---
# ==============================================================================
# Available values for 'BasedOnStyle' (Case-Sensitive):
# - LLVM: The default foundation style. Neutral, clean, and balanced.
# - Google: Follows the Google C++ Style Guide (highly strict, forces 2 spaces).
# - Chromium: Tailored for the Chromium browser project (uses 80-char limits).
# - Mozilla: Follows the Mozilla Corporation's layout rules.
# - WebKit: Standard layout style used by the WebKit browser engine.
# - GNU: Follows the GNU coding standards (very distinct, uses 2-space brace indents).
# - Microsoft: Matches Visual Studio's default formatting behavior.
# ==============================================================================

BasedOnStyle: Google
...
